{"tid":1201160,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"歐國聯最佳陣：C.朗拿度最高分領銜","createTime":"2019-06-11T03:01:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T07:30:25.000Z","uid":173952,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"cdd3e6111a166ce4362f9e2c62dc7a4d5b4c91a7","tid":1201160,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:01:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EvgSAJi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEvgSAJi.jpg&h=c243ee28&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"384715767ab3adb2d38601559eaac718ee106835","tid":1201160,"uid":51677,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:03:01.000Z","msg":"世一呢？"},{"pid":"23443e40385f0e312eb9a6f24f0020e24d8aea20","tid":1201160,"uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:06:48.000Z","msg":"C.朗拿度（C.Ronaldo）帶領葡萄牙拿到歐國聯冠軍，回首這一路走來的歷程，他感到十分滿意。<br />\n  「在過去十六年，我並沒有表現好差的時期，數據說明了一切，」C.朗拿度說，「在我職業生涯的大部分時間裡，我都展示出了這一點，無論人們怎麼說，數據是有說服力的。」<br />\n  C.朗拿度表示，自己喜歡拿獎盃，但並不沉迷其中。「顯然我喜歡獎盃，我不會撒謊，各種獎盃都有幫助，團隊的，個人的，但我並不沉迷於獎盃。」<br />\n<br />\n  當被問到今年金球獎的話題，C.朗拿度說：「我已經拿到了三個獎盃，我表現不錯，還能做什麼呢？」<br />\n  「我是否該拿金球獎？我不知道，這個問題我還是留給你們吧。你們是需要做出評判的人，而不是我來評判我自己。」"},{"pid":"f294c23571710a4ec4553750bb8f70c68770a5b4","tid":1201160,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:07:54.000Z","msg":"Pickford <br />\nDelph<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52441d1727a9d56ea7c003f6f58261956f0e3c6","tid":1201160,"uid":69125,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"f294c23571710a4ec4553750bb8f70c68770a5b4","tid":1201160,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:07:54.000Z","msg":"Pickford <br />\nDelph<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T03:12:07.000Z","msg":"又唔好笑pickford,守龍黎講佢係唔錯"},{"pid":"3ae597d05b5b4304b8ef0c22a2c65bc93223d274","tid":1201160,"uid":186292,"like":